OL,5, Retail sales are falling at a rate "not
OL,6, seen since the depths of the pandemic",
OL,7, as price rises hit household budgets, a
OL,8, UK retail body has said.               
OL,10,FShoppers are cutting back on white     
OL,11,Fgoods such as fridges and dishwashers  
OL,12,Fas well as opting for cheaper brands,  
OL,13,Fthe British Retail Consortium added.   
OL,15,FSales in shops and online have dropped 
OL,16,Ffor three months in a row, figures from
OL,17,Fthe BRC and accountants KPMG indicate. 
OL,19,FPrices in the UK are currently rising  
OL,20,Fat their fastest rate for 40 years.    
